text: Kylie Jenner's life is anything but normal. The reality star was been on television screens as the youngest child of the Kardashian-Jenner family since she was 9 years old. She never had the chance to opt out of fame — it was decided for her. Now, a decade later, she's still figuring out how to navigate the world under a microscope. And while she may seem like the least relatable person to the average young adult, there is one aspect in which she is just like us: she is obsessed with her crew of friends.
title: A Comprehensive Guide To Kylie Jenner's Clique
